    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid project or a budget-friendly daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The engine runs and the car is drivable, though it does have some high-mileage wear, including a minor oil leak and a suspension that feels a bit loose. Inside, the upholstery shows noticeable staining and some tearing on the driver's seat, and the exterior has several visible door dings and some fading paint on the hood. All major systems like the AC and radio are functional, but the vehicle would benefit from a comprehensive tune-up and some cosmetic TLC.",
